## Invariants

Things that must be true across all tickets. Violating one of these requires an ADR.

- _Example: "All external calls have a 5s timeout and a retry budget of 1."_
- _Example: "No user-facing string is hardcoded; all strings go through `i18n.t()`."_
- _Example: "State mutations happen only inside transactions."_

